WWW-Mechanize-XML version 0.02
=====================================

This is a subclass of WWW::Mechanize that provides an XML DOM accessor which
parses the contents of the response and returns it as an XML::LibXML::Document.
The motivation for developing this module was to facilitate testing of XML APIs
and XHTML web sites.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Test::More
  Test::Exception
  WWW::Mechanize
  XML::LibXML
  File::Temp

